wikipedia_page.main: Maxwell "Max" Eaves (born 31 May 1988 in Ascot, Berkshire) is an English athlete specialising in the pole vault.His personal best jumps are 5.62 metres outdoors (Loughborough 2014) and 5.64 metres indoors (Jablonec 2016).
